{"tid":1138522,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"手足們有冇留意開MAD ?","createTime":"2019-05-04T14:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T09:42:50.000Z","uid":105678,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4d545f7dddfda7fd90744cf5d642fc6a56ee1051","tid":1138522,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"MAD，姐係Music、Anime、動画(Douga)三字嘅結合，呢度「動画」嘅意思係指video。故名思意，MAD就係用動漫內容+音樂剪輯成嘅二次創作影片。MAD有好多種類，具體分成，靜止畫、動畫、音MAD、混合系四大類，依度講一講靜止畫類。<br />\n<br />\n靜止畫MAD即係用靜態圖片為原材料配合音樂堆砌而成嘅MAD，創作者一般用漫畫或者小說插圖加以動態效果，優點係保留原作味道，缺點技術需求較高同比較難製造動態感覺。<br />\n<br />\n用一拳超人做例子，如果係靜止畫就會有咁嘅效果：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v8teRVjsdr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv8teRVjsdr0&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=5cc1e804\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v8teRVjsdr0</a><br />\n【靜止畫MAD】一拳超人- 興趣使然的英雄<br />\n<br />\n反之，混合類會採用動畫+靜止畫嘅形式剪輯，畀觀眾一種動靜交錯嘅感覺，亦綜合咗靜止畫、動畫兩大類嘅優點，技術難度亦更高就好似咁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=isidXgvoXg0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DisidXgvoXg0&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=289f952b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=isidXgvoXg0</a><br />\n一拳超人: 深海王篇&mdash;不屈的正義<br />\n<br />\n至於音MAD，比起動畫本身，更加注意音效、音樂之間嘅結合，因為以鬼畜系為主，食用難度高，個人比較小留意，不過有一個幾出名嘅音MAD，唔知大家有冇睇過：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=psAgEdH6hbE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpsAgEdH6hbE&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=40a37bd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=psAgEdH6hbE</a><br />\n麥當勞叔叔洗腦影片 crazy MCdonalds(黑暗洗腦儀式版)<br />\n<br />\n最後拋下磚，個人覺得剪幾好嘅兩條MAD：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=51XfKTGIPR8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D51XfKTGIPR8&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=57f10df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=51XfKTGIPR8</a><br />\n銀/魂 「侠の鎖」【かぶき町四天王篇】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av1822333?from=search&amp;seid=1873316646328244493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav1822333%3Ffrom%3Dsearch%26seid%3D1873316646328244493&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=5797d963\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av1822333?from=search&amp;seid=1873316646328244493</a><br />\nFATE「上篇：命運」"},{"pid":"99c430b455ade76cdb87c8222bb6847691202910","tid":1138522,"uid":126835,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"善意打破0回覆"},{"pid":"1b376a082b4558377d3115a8cf97074f79be9018","tid":1138522,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99c430b455ade76cdb87c8222bb6847691202910","tid":1138522,"uid":126835,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"善意打破0回覆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"感謝你"},{"pid":"12f10a8de2a233ee630d54ab37d3161d86a061b9","tid":1138522,"uid":55029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"gchi"},{"pid":"f29e2d4298ea1f9189f0016bef12a4ca42efee89","tid":1138522,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IuSp_7g9tKw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIuSp_7g9tKw&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=0c48fa84\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IuSp_7g9tKw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lqazRJL5cs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlqazRJL5cs8&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=39083aa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lqazRJL5cs8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PveRMDcddnU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.